			â€¢ rÃ¶s > 100 ise mutlaka Ã¶nlem alÄ±nmasÄ± gerekir.
	
	Failure Modes, Effects, and Diagnostic Analysis (FMEDA)		-- Bu oranÄ±n 1'e yaklaÅŸmasÄ±, sistemin mÃ¼kemmele yaklaÅŸmasÄ± anlamÄ±nda
	Failure Mode, Effects, and Criticality Analysis (FMECA)
	
